#: ../../faq.rst:2
msgid "FAQ & Troubleshooting"
msgstr "常见问题与故障排除"

#: ../../faq.rst:4
msgid "Frequently asked questions and common issues."
msgstr "常见问题和一般故障排查。"

#: ../../faq.rst:7
msgid "General Questions"
msgstr "一般问题"

#: ../../faq.rst:10
msgid "Where is the output video saved?"
msgstr "输出视频保存在哪里？"

#: ../../faq.rst:12
msgid ""
"After calling ``render()``, the final MP4 is placed next to Manim's internal"
" render output, using the name you provided via ``video_name``:"
msgstr ""
"调用 ``render()`` 后，最终的 MP4 文件会放在 Manim 内部渲染输出目录中，文件名使用您通过 ``video_name`` "
"指定的名称："

#: ../../faq.rst:18
msgid ""
"The exact sub-directory (e.g. ``1080p60``) depends on Manim's current "
"quality configuration."
msgstr "具体的子目录（例如 ``1080p60``）取决于 Manim 当前的质量配置。"

#: ../../faq.rst:21
msgid "Cairo vs. OpenGL – which should I use?"
msgstr "Cairo 与 OpenGL – 应该使用哪个？"

#: ../../faq.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Cairo** (default, ``renderer='cairo'``) – CPU-based, works on virtually "
"all systems."
msgstr "**Cairo**\\ （默认，``renderer='cairo'``）– 基于 CPU，几乎可以在所有系统上运行。"

#: ../../faq.rst:24
msgid ""
"**OpenGL** (``renderer='opengl'``) – GPU-based, can be faster but requires "
"compatible graphics drivers."
msgstr "**OpenGL**\\ （``renderer='opengl'``）– 基于 GPU，可能更快，但需要兼容的显卡驱动。"

#: ../../faq.rst:26
msgid "If you encounter rendering errors with OpenGL, switch back to Cairo:"
msgstr "如果在使用 OpenGL 时遇到渲染错误，请切换回 Cairo："

#: ../../faq.rst:37
msgid "Does it support Chinese characters?"
msgstr "支持中文字符吗？"

#: ../../faq.rst:39
msgid ""
"Yes. CodeVideoRenderer bundles ``CodeVideoRendererFont`` to support CJK "
"characters. If you see garbled text, ensure your input code is valid UTF-8."
msgstr ""
"支持。CodeVideoRenderer 内置了 ``CodeVideoRendererFont`` 字体以支持 CJK "
"字符。如果出现乱码，请确保输入的代码是有效的 UTF-8 编码。"

#: ../../faq.rst:42
msgid "Common Issues"
msgstr "常见问题"

#: ../../faq.rst:45
msgid "FFmpeg not found"
msgstr "找不到 FFmpeg"

#: ../../faq.rst:47
msgid ""
"If rendering fails with an FFmpeg-related error, verify FFmpeg is installed "
"and available in your ``PATH``:"
msgstr "如果渲染失败并出现与 FFmpeg 相关的错误，请验证 FFmpeg 已安装并在 ``PATH`` 中可用："

#: ../../faq.rst:53
msgid ""
"If the command is not found, reinstall FFmpeg (see :doc:`installation`) and "
"restart your terminal."
msgstr "如果命令找不到，请重新安装 FFmpeg（参见 :doc:`installation`）并重启终端。"

#: ../../faq.rst:56
msgid "Invalid characters error"
msgstr "无效字符错误"

#: ../../faq.rst:58
msgid ""
"CodeVideoRenderer rejects the following characters because they can break "
"Manim's text layout:"
msgstr "CodeVideoRenderer 会拒绝以下字符，因为它们可能破坏 Manim 的文本布局："

#: ../../faq.rst:60
msgid "``\\r`` (carriage return)"
msgstr "``\\r``\\ （回车符）"

#: ../../faq.rst:61
msgid "``\\v`` (vertical tab)"
msgstr "``\\v``\\ （垂直制表符）"

#: ../../faq.rst:62
msgid "``\\f`` (form feed)"
msgstr "``\\f``\\ （换页符）"

#: ../../faq.rst:64
msgid ""
"If your code contains these (often copied from certain editors), replace "
"them with regular spaces or newlines before passing the string to "
"``CameraFollowCursorCV``."
msgstr ""
"如果您的代码中包含这些字符（通常是从某些编辑器复制而来），请在将字符串传递给 ``CameraFollowCursorCV`` "
"之前将其替换为普通空格或换行符。"

#: ../../faq.rst:67
msgid "Code is cut off or too large"
msgstr "代码被截断或太大"

#: ../../faq.rst:69
msgid ""
"If your code block overflows the visible area or the camera zoom feels "
"wrong, adjust ``camera_scale``:"
msgstr "如果您的代码块超出了可视区域，或者相机缩放感觉不对，请调整 ``camera_scale``："

#: ../../faq.rst:80
msgid ""
"Values smaller than the default ``0.5`` zoom the camera out; larger values "
"zoom in."
msgstr "小于默认值 ``0.5`` 的值会缩小相机视野；更大的值会放大。"

#: ../../faq.rst:83
msgid "How do I suppress console output during rendering?"
msgstr "如何在渲染期间抑制控制台输出？"

#: ../../faq.rst:85
msgid "Pass ``output=False`` to :meth:`~.render`:"
msgstr "向 :meth:`~.render` 传递 ``output=False``："

#: ../../faq.rst:91
msgid ""
"This disables progress bars and timing logs while still producing the video "
"file."
msgstr "这会禁用进度条和计时日志，同时仍然生成视频文件。"

#: ../../faq.rst:94
msgid "Why does Manim caching not work?"
msgstr "为什么 Manim 缓存不起作用？"

#: ../../faq.rst:96
msgid ""
"CodeVideoRenderer internally sets ``config.disable_caching = True`` to "
"prevent stale cache files from interfering with the code-typing animation. "
"This is intentional and not a bug."
msgstr ""
"CodeVideoRenderer 在内部设置 ``config.disable_caching = "
"True``，以防止过时的缓存文件干扰代码输入动画。这是有意设计的，并非 bug。"

#: ../../faq.rst:99
msgid "Why is my code slightly misaligned vertically?"
msgstr "为什么我的代码在垂直方向上略有错位？"

#: ../../faq.rst:101
msgid ""
"Certain characters (``acegmnopqrsuvwxyz+,-.:;<=>_~``) trigger a known Manim "
"text-layout alignment bug. CodeVideoRenderer automatically applies a "
"workaround offset (:data:`~.CODE_OFFSET`) for these characters. If you still"
" see issues, try adjusting ``camera_scale`` or avoid those characters in "
"critical positions."
msgstr ""
"某些字符（``acegmnopqrsuvwxyz+,-.:;<=>_~``）会触发一个已知的 Manim 文本布局对齐 "
"bug。CodeVideoRenderer 会自动为这些字符应用变通偏移量（:data:`~.CODE_OFFSET`）。如果仍然看到问题，请尝试调整 "
"``camera_scale``，或在关键位置避免使用这些字符。"

#: ../../faq.rst:104
msgid "Are tabs expanded? Can I change the tab size?"
msgstr "Tab 会被扩展吗？我可以更改 tab 大小吗？"

#: ../../faq.rst:106
msgid ""
"Yes — tabs are always expanded to spaces using a tab size of ``4`` (the "
":data:`~.DEFAULT_TAB_WIDTH` constant). Currently this value cannot be "
"changed at runtime; if you need a different tab size, preprocess your code "
"string before passing it to :class:`~.CameraFollowCursorCV`."
msgstr ""
"是的 — tab 总是使用 ``4`` 的空格大小进行扩展（即 :data:`~.DEFAULT_TAB_WIDTH` "
"常量）。目前该值无法在运行时更改；如果您需要不同的 tab 大小，请在将代码字符串传递给 :class:`~.CameraFollowCursorCV`"
" 之前进行预处理。"

#: ../../faq.rst:109
msgid "What happens if ``video_name`` is empty?"
msgstr "如果 ``video_name`` 为空会发生什么？"

#: ../../faq.rst:111
msgid ""
"The constructor raises ``ValueError(\"video_name must be provided\")`` if "
"``video_name`` is empty or falsy. Always provide a non-empty string."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``video_name`` 为空或为假值，构造函数会抛出 ``ValueError(\"video_name must be "
"provided\")``。请始终提供非空字符串。"

#: ../../faq.rst:114
msgid "Rendering is slow"
msgstr "渲染速度慢"

#: ../../faq.rst:116
msgid "Try ``renderer='opengl'`` if you have a compatible GPU."
msgstr "如果您有兼容的 GPU，请尝试使用 ``renderer='opengl'``。"

#: ../../faq.rst:117
msgid "Reduce the code length or split it into multiple shorter videos."
msgstr "缩短代码长度，或将其拆分为多个较短的视频。"

#: ../../faq.rst:118
msgid ""
"Ensure you are not running inside a very slow virtual machine without GPU "
"passthrough."
msgstr "确保您没有在没有 GPU 直通功能的非常慢的虚拟机中运行。"
